15
00:01:20,400 --> 00:01:26,000
Oh, that's difficult. I know that Spain produces a lot, but I think I'm going to go with Italy.

16
00:01:26,000 --> 00:01:31,200
Okay, well we'll find out if that's the right answer at the end of the programme.

17
00:01:31,200 --> 00:01:35,200
Now lots of us are careful about the amount of fat we eat.

18
00:01:35,200 --> 00:01:43,200
We might avoid fast food and treats like chocolate or cake, but lots of the fat we eat comes from the oils we cook with.

19
00:01:43,200 --> 00:01:50,000
Yes and some expensive oils claim to contain other vitamins that are good for us, but are these claims true?

20
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:51,359
