45
00:04:07,600 --> 00:04:10,000
What do you think, Nita? What might justify the price tag?

46
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:18,639
Certainly avocado oil is good for all the reasons mentioned. But is it worth justifying the cost?

47
00:04:19,519 --> 00:04:25,040
