49
00:04:33,199 --> 00:04:37,920
wonder this and that. And it's just all I'm afraid hogwash.

50
00:04:39,039 --> 00:04:44,240
Nita says that avocado oil does have some health benefits but she's not sure they are worth the

51
00:04:44,240 --> 00:04:50,560
