54
00:05:02,800 --> 00:05:07,360
hogwash. They are nonsense and products are not worth spending money on.

55
00:05:07,360 --> 00:05:12,400
Okay, maybe I'll stick to my olive oil then. And that reminds me of your question, Neil.

56
00:05:12,400 --> 00:05:15,920
Yes, I asked you which country produces the most olive oil.

57
00:05:16,480 --> 00:05:22,000
And I said Italy. And I'm afraid you are wrong. No.

58
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:27,519
